Tamasheq: Issunfa daɣ tăkerkurt n idraren win ăfella n Mekka, ǝkahhăm ǝlla daɣ aǧilăl ful eddunet ɣăred. 
English: The city of Mekka was encircled by the Nile and the Red Sea, and the city of Medina was encircled by the Red Sea and the Arabian Sea.
